channel.description:
Well it has been awhile since I was coding these servers, but im back ;D
I am starting a new server, DeVScape, which is in desperate need of Mods(GM's) and Coders! If you are interested in helping out, contact my msn: a_ryan-helmick@hotmail.com , or simply reply to this post.
Thanks!
